These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  social-worker, accountant
1. the social-worker is on the left of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Job   | social-worker | accountant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, whist
1. the person playing whist is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Game   | monopoly | whist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, january
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Birthday   | january | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-4::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, alhambra
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |
| Cigar   | alhambra | pall-mall |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-5::.
